A4.text: Janet Damita Jo Jackson (born May 16, 1966) is an American singer, songwriter, actress, and dancer.

A5.text: The tenth and youngest child of the Jackson family, Jackson starred in multiple television shows throughout the 1970s and early 1980s, including Good Times, Diff'rent Strokes and Fame.
